## SClassmap

## Usage

Here's how to use our implementation:

```js
import __SClassmap from '@coffeekraken/s-classmap';

const classmap = new __SClassmap({
    map: {
        'my-cool-class': 's0',
        // etc...   
    }
});

const html = `<div class="my-cool-class">
    Hello world
</div>`;

const finalHtml = classmap.patchHtml(html);
// <div class="s0">
//      Hello world
// </div>
```

